Our home is on a Estate Lot called the  Key Largo with 3 Bedrooms and a Den and 3 Full Baths, Gourmet Kitchen with upgraded GE appliances,Gas Cook Top and Double Ovens,  Kitchen Custom Cabinets with Quartz Counter Top. Engineered Flooring Through Out, Bianco Carrera Tile in all bathrooms and Laundry, Crown Molding Through Out, Silhouettes Window Treatments, Crystal Sconces in Dining with Crystal Chandelier with Dimmers through out Living and Kitchen area, Wood Framed mirrors in All Bathrooms and Seamless Glass shower doors in all bathrooms, Built in Closet System in Master Bedroom, Hurricane Impact Glass Through out, Surround Sound in Living Area and Sono's set up with  Outdoor Speaker  System, 2 year warranty on Home Appliances, Home Storm Surge Protector, Epoxy painted Floor in Garage with shelving, Screened in Lanai and Salt Water Heated Pool & Spa with Indoor Pentair Touch Pad and colored light system for pool and this is ALL Facing West for a Beautiful Sunset at night.
